title: Drew Brees to return in 2020, Top 100 Free Agents, XFL Evaluations through 2 weeks (Football 2/19)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco to discuss the return of Drew Brees (3:15) and what it means for the Saints, Teddy Bridgewater/Taysom hill and the upcoming QB free agent market. The guys also discuss DJ Humphries new deal with the Cardinals (13:50), before analyzing Pete's list of the Top 100 NFL Free Agents (17:30). Then, Cody Benjamin joins the podcast to talk about the XFL through its first two weeks (36:00). How much will quarterback performance dictate the success of the league? Will and Cody take a look back at Week 2 before breaking down best gambling and DFS plays for Week 3.

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
